{
  "stem": "15694.7",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, ending the last reel, I was marching in a group frantically thinking, I must not go wherever they will lead me because my father isn't here.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I will not go-- I'm not going to be parted with my father.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I knew very well the dangers-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--in doing so, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, we were marching, and from the assembly place onto the main street which-- it was an old-- by the way, the camp was built on an old Jewish cemetery, and the street was called by the Poles Jerusalemska.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I find a bit of mockery in there as well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were walking on the gravestones.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, this is only by the by.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this street, we reached.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And as we reached the street, I could see there were was-- for the first time, I could see-- we turned right, and towards a little house which had some light in front.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in front of that house, there were the SS men and some Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And where these people were, the columns turned again left into-- across the street into what I would call a mini camp.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This camp was wired anyway.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Wires-- wires surround barracks, wires surround the working place, and wires about, you know, everywhere.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there I call it a mini camp, because I hadn't seen it before.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I think there were-- where the Poles actually lived on-- on the sketch map.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Only on the sketch-- sort of on a sketch map, they must have been for the later story, which is to come, that the wire in the back must have been extended.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I'll tell that story later, what it has-- that time, it was-- it was something small-- somewhat smaller.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
